{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"htnb0jl9cmmsba0gaxoj8e1","title":"Deploy-Smart-Contracts-Using-Hardhat","desc":"","updated":1668313452212,"created":1668313445238,"custom":{},"fname":"blockchain.Deploy-Smart-Contracts-Using-Hardhat","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"c7d612594f0d24a8264d38d21994c714","links":[],"anchors":{"deploy-smartcontract":{"type":"header","text":"Deploy smartcontract","value":"deploy-smartcontract","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"install-hardhat":{"type":"header","text":"Install hardhat","value":"install-hardhat","line":9,"column":0,"depth":2},"deploy-contract":{"type":"header","text":"Deploy contract","value":"deploy-contract","line":24,"column":0,"depth":2},"create-onchain-account":{"type":"header","text":"Create onchain account","value":"create-onchain-account","line":26,"column":0,"depth":3},"install-dependencies":{"type":"header","text":"Install dependencies","value":"install-dependencies","line":30,"column":0,"depth":3},"get-fund":{"type":"header","text":"Get fund","value":"get-fund","line":39,"column":0,"depth":3},"deploy":{"type":"header","text":"Deploy","value":"deploy","line":45,"column":0,"depth":3},"verify":{"type":"header","text":"Verify","value":"verify","line":57,"column":0,"depth":3}},"children":[],"parent":"u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"deploy-smart-contracts-using-hardhat\">Deploy-Smart-Contracts-Using-Hardhat<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#deploy-smart-contracts-using-hardhat\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"deploy-smartcontract\">Deploy smartcontract<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#deploy-smartcontract\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"install-hardhat\">Install hardhat<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#install-hardhat\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Install NodeJs: <a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-node-js-on-ubuntu-20-04#option-3-installing-node-using-the-node-version-manager\">https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-node-js-on-ubuntu-20-04#option-3-installing-node-using-the-node-version-manager</a>\n<ul>\n<li><code>curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.2/install.sh | bash</code></li>\n<li><code>source ~/.bashrc</code>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<pre><code>export NVM_DIR=\"$HOME/.nvm\"  \n  [ -s \"$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh\" ] &#x26;&#x26; \\. \"$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh\"  # This loads nvm \n  [ -s \"$NVM_DIR/bash_completion\" ] &#x26;&#x26; \\. \"$NVM_DIR/bash_completion\"  # This loads nvm bash_completion \n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>nvm install v16.18.0</code></li>\n<li><code>nvm use v16.18.0</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Ref: <a href=\"https://hardhat.org/hardhat-runner/docs/getting-started#installation\">https://hardhat.org/hardhat-runner/docs/getting-started#installation</a>\n<ul>\n<li><code>npm install --save-dev hardhat</code> </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"deploy-contract\">Deploy contract<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#deploy-contract\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"create-onchain-account\">Create onchain account<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#create-onchain-account\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://vanity-eth.tk/\">https://vanity-eth.tk/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"install-dependencies\">Install dependencies<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#install-dependencies\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code>npm install --save-dev @openzeppelin/contracts\nnpm install --save-dev dotenv`\nnpm install --save-dev @nomiclabs/hardhat-ethers \nnpm install --save-dev @nomiclabs/hardhat-etherscan\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"get-fund\">Get fund<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#get-fund\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>faucet:\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://faucet.polygon.technology/\">https://faucet.polygon.technology/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mumbaifaucet.com/\">https://mumbaifaucet.com/</a> </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"deploy\">Deploy<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#deploy\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Rename contract\n<ul>\n<li>update the Contract.deploy(<name>, <symbol>, <uri>) </uri></symbol></name></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Update ENV value\n<ul>\n<li>API_URL: node API URL</li>\n<li>PRIVATE_KEY: deploy private key</li>\n<li>ETHERSCAN_API: etherscan's API_KEY of deploying network </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>RUN\n<ul>\n<li><code>npx hardhat run --network mumbai scripts/deploy.js</code> </li>\n<li>Output: <code>Contract deployed to address: &#x3C;contract address></code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"verify\">Verify<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#verify\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Add ETHERSCAN_API (api_key)</li>\n<li>Update <code>args.js</code> to match the deployed contract constructor's value</li>\n<li><code>npx hardhat verify ----constructor-args ./scripts/args.js --network mumbai &#x3C;address></code></li>\n<li>Ref: <a href=\"https://hardhat.org/hardhat-runner/plugins/nomiclabs-hardhat-etherscan#complex-arguments\">https://hardhat.org/hardhat-runner/plugins/nomiclabs-hardhat-etherscan#complex-arguments</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3erv